<emphasis id="B90648316F3DFFD00996F8E0FD5CF8C6" bold="true" box="[727,748,1824,1850]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">A</emphasis>
. Head, ♀ from Colombia. 
<emphasis id="B90648316F3DFFD00F07F8E0FBEAF8C6" bold="true" box="[1094,1114,1824,1850]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">B</emphasis>
