<emphasis id="B90648316F3DFFD009D9F883FD1DF8A1" bold="true" box="[664,685,1859,1885]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">C</emphasis>
. Paratype prior to capture, ♀, Ecuador (inner vertical and postocellar bristles visible). 
<emphasis id="B90648316F3DFFD0095CF8A6FD82F87C" bold="true" box="[541,562,1894,1920]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">D</emphasis>
